[src:spherical-harmonics/spherical-harmonics-p02] This expression is valid for both real and complex harmonics.
[src:spherical-harmonics/spherical-harmonics-p02] The result can be proven analytically, using the properties of the Poisson kernel in the unit ball, or geometrically by applying a rotation to the vector **y** so that it points along the *z*-axis, and then directly calculating the right-hand side.
